    "content": "# Title: The Phase: Shattering the Illusion of Reality\r\n\r\nBook reference with attached EPUB file.\r\n\r\n![[The_Phase_-_Shattering_the__Z-Library.epub]]\r\n\r\n## Key Points (from vault notes)\r\n\r\nReferenced in [[Notes/The Illusion of Objective Reality|The Illusion of Objective Reality]] — the book argues that the reality we experience is 'just' neurons firing in the prefrontal cortex, creating a model of reality from sensory stimuli. Michael Raduga claims that The Phase *is* reality, and reality is The Phase.\r\n\r\n## Related\r\n\r\n- [[Notes/The Illusion of Objective Reality|The Illusion of Objective Reality]]\r\n- [[Notes/Subjective Reality|Subjective Reality]]\r\n- [[Notes/Objective Reality|Objective Reality]]\n\n#resource #moc/philosophy",
